column2: SELECT SpecObj.specObjID, SpecObj.z, SpecObj.ra, SpecObj.dec, zooSpec.p_el, zooSpec.p_cw, zooSpec.p_acw, zooSpec.p_mg, zooSpec.spiral, zooSpec.elliptical FROM SpecObj, zooSpec WHERE zooSpec.specObjID = SpecObj.specObjID AND SpecObj.class = # AND SpecObj.sourceType = # AND (zooSpec.p_el > # OR zooSpec.p_cw > # OR zooSpec.p_acw > # OR zooSpec.p_mg > #) AND zooSpec.uncertain = # ORDER BY SpecObj.z DESC
